divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband and I were traveling toward home on man of war drive Lexington Kentucky when we saw an orbicular bright white light traveling at high speeds from north to south crossing man of war Boulevard it was not a meteor as it did not have a meteor trail, it was moving at a rapid speed faster than plane or helicopter and disappeared within 50 seconds of sighting. There were several other cars I noted that slowed their speed to look at the object.
